        <div class="container">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <p style="line-height: 1.8; color: #666;">
                        Founded in 2020, our store has grown from a small local shop to one of the most trusted Apple retailers in the region. We believe in providing not just products, but complete solutions that enhance our customers' digital lifestyle.
                    </p>
                    <p style="line-height: 1.8; color: #666; margin-top: 1rem;">
                        Our commitment to excellence, customer satisfaction, and technical expertise has earned us numerous accolades and a loyal customer base that continues to grow year after year.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="/images/about-store.jpg" alt="Our Store" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
